org.openimaj.vis.general

Class ChronologicalScrollingBarVisualisation3D

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.vis.general.ChronologicalScrollingBarVisualisation3D
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visualisation<double[]>, VisualisationImageProvider

    public class ChronologicalScrollingBarVisualisation3D
extends Object
implements Visualisation<double[]>
    A chronological bar chart, where each time you add a data point, the visualisation is moved along and another set of data is added to the 3D visualisation. Data must therefore be one dimensional.
    Author:
    David Dupplaw (dpd@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
